title: (Weds Early Bird) Amy and Eddie Compete for The Crying Boy Doll + Restless Road Performs a Medley and Their Kane Brown Connection
itunes:title: (Weds Early Bird) Amy and Eddie Compete for The Crying Boy Doll + Restless Road Performs a Medley and Their Kane Brown Connection
description:
Amy and Eddie claimed yesterday that they don’t believe objects can be haunted. But now we ordered a haunted doll. They compete and the loser has to take it home for a week. New group Restless Road stop by to perform a medley, their new song and how they have a crazy connection with Kane Brown.
